-- Malaysia's Maxis to undertake $767 mln in Islamic financing 
-- By Al-Zaquan Amer Hamzah
-- Wed Apr 02, 2014 07:29AM EDT
-- None



KUALA LUMPUR, April 2 (Reuters) - Malaysia's Maxis Bhd <MXSC.KL> will undertake 2.5 billion ringgit ($766.5 million) in loans to refinance its debt and fund its capital needs, it said in an announcement to the stock exchange on Wednesday.

